data.description:
Welcome home!
An inviting 3-bedroom home on a sizable lot is waiting for you! With the added benefits of a detached garage with custom shelving and a storage building, this property fulfills your desires for both comfort and functionality. Take advantage of the abundant space for leisure, gardening, and creative endeavors! Recent updates include a NEW roof, all new trim throughout the interior of the home, exterior paint and siding. The dual driveway provides ample parking for your vehicles, boat, and RV!! Tucked away from the hustle and bustle of the city, yet still close to amenities and just minutes from Lake Murray!!
